><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0021@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0022@@</p></li></ul><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0023@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_e8ed28a6bd\">@@body:0024@@</h2><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0025@@</p><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0026@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0027@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0028@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0029@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0030@@</p></li></ul><div class=\"intercom-container\"><img src=\"https://govocal---eu.intercom-attachments.eu/i/o/nfttr45j/90373791/b3e91d278f7dc46539a6790b8cb4/upload_7145987143271233237.png?expires=1781870400&amp;signature=487406e2b1efd6951be0d6056b5eec892eb6207e33321986a6e109e12ffbc4a7&amp;req=2dVswlv9pTZk2hj99dpg6l0DcI5a7hAVo5uwLtnSeRJk0e5Rp67%2F5nHPz0EH%0Al77SNbMDUiCQiysIAPBLwsjm%0A\"/></div><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_c633ed9d8a\">@@body:0031@@</h2><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0032@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0033@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0034@@</p></li></ul><h2 id=\"h_73a946a1b7\">@@body:0035@@</h2><ol><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0036@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0037@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0038@@</p></li></ol><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0039@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0040@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"h_61904e0b42\">@@body:0041@@</h2><ul><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0042@@</p></li><li><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0043@@</p></li></ul><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0044@@</p><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"h_b34c662fdc\">@@body:0045@@</h1><div class=\"intercom-interblocks-table-container\"><table role=\"presentation\"><tbody><tr><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0046@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0047@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0048@@</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0049@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0050@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0051@@</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0052@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0053@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0054@@</p></td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</td><td><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</td><td><p class=\"no-margin\"></p>\n</td></tr><tr><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0055@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0056@@</p></td><td><p class=\"no-margin\">@@body:0057@@</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "segments": {
    "title": {
      "field": "title",
      "text": "Setting up SSO login options and user/identity verification methods",
      "hash": "3c2c555aa5f8"
    },
    "description": {
      "field": "description",
      "text": "",
      "hash": "e3b0c44298fc"
    },
    "body:0001": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "What are SSO and verification methods?",
      "hash": "000b8e53dc1c"
    },
    "body:0002": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "By default, users must confirm their email via a code to create an account. This manual verification can be a barrier to participation. With SSO (Single Sign-On) options like Google, Facebook, or Microsoft Entra, users can register and log in with a single click, making the process faster and more user-friendly.",
      "hash": "707f430c8a14"
    },
    "body:0003": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "For projects that require stronger identity verification, you can add:",
      "hash": "736acb5cd1ba"
    },
    "body:0004": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Unique code verification for specific participants",
      "hash": "938b70d2a2f2"
    },
    "body:0005": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "National ID authentication systems (available in select countries)",
      "hash": "dbf661c90cf9"
    },
    "body:0006": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Access to these features depends on your subscription plan.",
      "hash": "3a95091685e3"
    },
    "body:0007": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Different SSO and verification methods",
      "hash": "1201ab3b01ee"
    },
    "body:0008": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Google and Facebook login (free)",
      "hash": "c72fb060d527"
    },
    "body:0009": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "These options provide an easy, low-barrier login experience. When enabled:",
      "hash": "0fdc4250fc12"
    },
    "body:0010": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Users can register or log in by clicking a single button.",
      "hash": "4bb7201e2df0"
    },
    "body:0011": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Their email is automatically verified through the selected provider (Google or Facebook).",
      "hash": "c3fc095ccbbb"
    },
    "body:0012": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "To enable these options, contact the Support team using the chat bubble in your platform.",
      "hash": "80cb99ae18d5"
    },
    "body:0013": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Microsoft Entra login (with additional fees)",
      "hash": "f4adf0531dfc"
    },
    "body:0014": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "This is ideal if your organization already uses Microsoft accounts internally.",
      "hash": "587378e2eac7"
    },
    "body:0015": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Options:",
      "hash": "367431fd664b"
    },
    "body:0016": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Add Microsoft Entra login to a public page for general use (as a log in option or through a link below the log in options as shown in the images below)",
      "hash": "522f50128ae4"
    },
    "body:0017": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Restrict it to a private URL visible only to your staff",
      "hash": "57bfb7f4c436"
    },
    "body:0018": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "To set it up, send the following to Support:",
      "hash": "bd4de1b29b3f"
    },
    "body:0019": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Directory (tenant) ID",
      "hash": "1dc4abe27594"
    },
    "body:0020": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Application (client) ID",
      "hash": "576111a7aee1"
    },
    "body:0021": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Login mechanism name (e.g., “Sign up with city account”)",
      "hash": "21587bb63e12"
    },
    "body:0022": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "(Optional) Logo URL for the login button",
      "hash": "c2cd92bd6c85"
    },
    "body:0023": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Support will activate the login option for you.",
      "hash": "84748f678667"
    },
    "body:0024": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "National identity authentication systems",
      "hash": "8ac90433a8b1"
    },
    "body:0025": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "We support integration with several national systems for secure identity verification:",
      "hash": "3a3703ccea2a"
    },
    "body:0026": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Belgium:</b> CSAM (e-ID, itsme)",
      "hash": "9900f1d451d5"
    },
    "body:0027": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>France:</b> FranceConnect",
      "hash": "787e98eb1382"
    },
    "body:0028": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Chile:</b> COW",
      "hash": "7dd7ce6c3ee3"
    },
    "body:0029": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Denmark:</b> NemID",
      "hash": "69aa499b9232"
    },
    "body:0030": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "<b>Austria</b>: ID-Austria",
      "hash": "b0fd4253eb76"
    },
    "body:0031": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Common use cases:",
      "hash": "abbf5c9a65df"
    },
    "body:0032": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Limit participation to citizens of a specific country",
      "hash": "20235c396809"
    },
    "body:0033": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Prevent users from creating multiple accounts",
      "hash": "7d692e06e35a"
    },
    "body:0034": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Ensure participants register using their real identity",
      "hash": "9981beb586a6"
    },
    "body:0035": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Setup process:",
      "hash": "6761e8bcd447"
    },
    "body:0036": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Contact Support at least 2–3 months in advance to plan the integration.",
      "hash": "d5b847219183"
    },
    "body:0037": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Our team will work with you and national authorities to get the necessary permissions.",
      "hash": "5c66bedefa99"
    },
    "body:0038": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Once configured, users will verify themselves via the national system when registering or attempting to interact with a restricted project.",
      "hash": "10ff20e44e40"
    },
    "body:0039": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "⚠️ We do not store or access national ID numbers. The national system handles all authentication.",
      "hash": "bf8fec9a5175"
    },
    "body:0040": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "⚠️ We may receive basic information (like first name, last name, email) to populate the user’s profile, additional data like age or residence is not transferred.",
      "hash": "63ac431ff44b"
    },
    "body:0041": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "After setup:",
      "hash": "9c4fb945ff78"
    },
    "body:0042": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Create a <b>smart group</b> for verified users via national authentication.",
      "hash": "3ce6cad7e0d1"
    },
    "body:0043": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Limit project visibility or participation based on this group.",
      "hash": "7ac79d1363f8"
    },
    "body:0044": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "In France, <b>FranceConnect</b> can also be used as an SSO method, users don’t need to create a new account on your platform.",
      "hash": "f89a08370826"
    },
    "body:0045": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "When to use which method?",
      "hash": "0ad95042b727"
    },
    "body:0046": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Method",
      "hash": "52a0f9b65b27"
    },
    "body:0047": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Ideal for",
      "hash": "f7cb5647f0c5"
    },
    "body:0048": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Requirements",
      "hash": "e0cdd07f6a27"
    },
    "body:0049": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Google/Facebook SSO",
      "hash": "c38501810eb9"
    },
    "body:0050": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Fast and simple sign-up",
      "hash": "621b1715ee4b"
    },
    "body:0051": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "No setup required beyond Support request",
      "hash": "839f04bff079"
    },
    "body:0052": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Microsoft Entra SSO",
      "hash": "acd5d48e7340"
    },
    "body:0053": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Staff or internal login",
      "hash": "015d2478b14b"
    },
    "body:0054": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Microsoft Tenant + App ID + Setup",
      "hash": "d6ff959d0610"
    },
    "body:0055": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "National Authentication",
      "hash": "1c78e4653aa0"
    },
    "body:0056": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Secure ID verification for citizens",
      "hash": "2bc3fbc078ea"
    },
    "body:0057": {
      "field": "body",
      "text": "Country-specific setup + early planning",
      "hash": "f87811513cd1"
    }
  }
}